Question Title: Tax Calculator

Question Description:

You are building a simple tax calculator program for a financial application. 
Write a Java program that calculates the total tax amount based on the income and tax brackets.

The tax brackets are defined as follows:

路 Income up to $10,000: 5% tax

路 Income from $10,001 to $20,000: 10% tax

路 Income from $20,001 to $50,000: 15% tax

路 Income above $50,000: 20% tax

Sample Input 1:

8000

Sample Output 1:

400.0

Sample Input 2:

30000

Sample Output 2:

4500.0